      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LESTER BANNER (1) boasts a strong record this course with two wins and two minors from six tries. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (19.89) in a Restricted WIN last time at this track. With a clean break looks hard to beat. MCCLUGGAGE (7) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (19.15) at Q Straight. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Expected to be in the finish again. FRAGILE FRANKIE (2) turned in a solid run last start over 520m at Q Parklands finishing 4th and beaten only 2 lengths (30.06). Comes out of a hot form race last start. Great chance to atone. BARDWELL (3) is another with top-three prospects.",
